name: Sales Tracking
query:
select name as "SO#:Data:220",
sales_channel as "Channel:Data:120",

po_no as "PO#:Data:120",
shipping_service as "Shipping Service:Data:120",
shipment_details as "Tracking:Data:120",
	shipment_cost as "Shipping Amount:Data:200",
	transaction_date as "Date:Data:220"
	
from `tabSales Order` order by creation DESC;
